# Metadata
################

### Get all metadata by directory ID
GET http://localhost:18085/api/v1/directories/d43e6d85-e0e8-4b01-ad9e-2926db994c5e/metadata

### Get metadata by directory ID and key
GET http://localhost:18085/api/v1/directories/d43e6d85-e0e8-4b01-ad9e-2926db994c5e/metadata/type

### Create metadata
POST http://localhost:18085/api/v1/directories/d43e6d85-e0e8-4b01-ad9e-2926db994c5e/metadata
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type": "list"
}

### Update metadata
PUT http://localhost:18085/api/v1/directories/d43e6d85-e0e8-4b01-ad9e-2926db994c5e/metadata
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type": "List"
}

### Delete directory
DELETE  http://localhost:18085/api/v1/directories/d43e6d85-e0e8-4b01-ad9e-2926db994c5e/metadata/type